2013-12-14  Sam Truzjan  <pxqr.sta@gmail.com>

	* 0.4.2.0: Override default fixity for operators: previously it
	has been impossible to mix bencode Get operators ((<$>!), (<$>?),
	(<*>!), (<*>?)) with applicative operators ((<$>), (<*>)).

